lead_paragraph: A New-York correspondent of The Washington Union has the following paragraph, which has interest from the light which it may possibly throw upon the political future: "With the reunion of the democratic party, we observe the introduction of a new element into our federal politics, or rather the suggestion of a new candidate for the presidential chair.
